Class TestContentInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • TestContentInfo
  • public class TestContentInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements JUnit tests for the methods of the ContentInfo class. The methods for this implementation test all the ContentInfo methods for each type of content.
    Since:
    2020-01-29
    Version:
    2
    Author:
    litchi
